MATT: Yeah, we're gonna get to that right now.

01:23:46.970 --> 01:23:52.306
You did get a message from Allura that tells you 
that the ritual is successful. Scanlan is alive.

01:23:52.306 --> 01:23:54.791
LAURA: (excited noise)

